<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <link rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.googleapis.com' />
    <link rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.gstatic.com' crossorigin />
    <link
      href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap'
      rel='stylesheet'
    />
    <title>Welcome to Our App</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4;"
  >
    <div
      style='max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;'
    >
      <header
        style='background-color: #1e1e1e; text-align: center; padding: 20px;'
      >
        <h1 style='color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px;'>Welcome to Our
          App!</h1>
      </header>
      <div style='padding: 20px; text-align: left;'>
        <p style='font-size: 18px; color: #333;'>
          Hi
          {{name}},
        </p>
        <p style='font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5;'>
          We're thrilled to have you on board! By joining our app, you're now
          part of a community that's dedicated to making life easier, more
          connected, and more enjoyable.
        </p>
        <p style='font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5;'>
          Here are some things you can do right away:
        </p>
        <ul
          style='padding-left: 20px; color: #555; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;'
        >
          <li>Explore the features of our app.</li>
          <li>Invite your friends and family to join the experience.</li>
          <li>Reach out to our support team for any assistance.</li>
        </ul>
        <p style='font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5;'>
          If you have any questions or feedback, don’t hesitate to get in touch.
          We’re here to make your experience amazing.
        </p>
        <div style='text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;'>
          <a
            href='{{link}}'
            style='
              background-color: #1e1e1e;
              color: #ffffff;
              text-decoration: none;
              padding: 10px 20px;
              font-size: 16px;
              border-radius: 4px;
            '
          >Get Started</a>
        </div>
        <p style='font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5;'>
          Thanks for joining, and welcome aboard!
        </p>
        <p style='font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5;'>
          Warm regards,<br />
          The BARU Team
        </p>
      </div>
      <footer
        style='background-color: #757575; text-align: center; padding: 10px; font-size: 12px; color: #fff;'
      >
        <p>You are receiving this email because you signed up for our app.</p>
        <p>
          If you didn’t sign up, please ignore this email, or contact us at
          <a
            href='mailto:support@yourapp.com'
            style='color: #1e1e1e;'
          >support@yourapp.com</a>.
        </p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>